LAS CONFESIONES DE SCHMIDT

2
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:46,374
FELIZ JUBILACION WARREN SCHMIDT

3
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:56,086
HOGAR DE DOS NOVILLOS CAMPEONES
DE 1969

4
00:03:18,778 --> 00:03:21,214
